<bibRefCitation id="737B4B6A7D18FFE06116FE86FAEBAD0A" author="Selys" box="[1148,1306,325,347]" firstAuthor="Selys" page="60" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="1" refId="ref20498" refString="Selys - Longchamps, M. E. (1886) Revision du synopsis des Agrionides, Premiere partie comprenant les legions Pseudostigma- Podagrion - Platycnemis et Protoneura. Memoires couronnes et Autres Memoires publies par Academie Royale des Sciences, des Lettres et des Beaux - Arts de Belgique, 38 (4), 1 + iv + 2 - 233." type="journal article" year="1886">Selys 1886: 60</bibRefCitation>
(diagnosis); 
<bibRefCitation id="737B4B6A7D18FFE065ADFEA0FE59AD28" author="Williamson" box="[199,424,355,377]" firstAuthor="Williamson" page="29" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 87" refId="ref20635" refString="Williamson, E. B. (1919) Results of the University of Michigan - Williamson Expedition to Colombia, 1916 - 1917. IV. Notes on species of the genus Heteragrion Selys with description of new species (Odonata). Occasional Papers Museum Of Zoology, University of Michigan, nº 68, 1 - 87." type="journal article" year="1919">Williamson 1919: 29</bibRefCitation>
