<bibRefCitation id="737B4B6A7D18FFE066E7FDBBFB58AEDF" author="Garrison" box="[909,1193,632,654]" etAl="et al" firstAuthor="Garrison" page="88 - 89" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" refId="ref20019" refString="Garrison, R. W., von Ellenrieder, N. &amp; Louton, J. A. (2010) Damselfly Genera of the New World: An Illustrated and Annotated Key to the Zygoptera. The Johns Hopkins University Press, 490 pp." type="book" year="2010">Garrison et al 2010: 88–89</bibRefCitation>
